<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contrato de Préstamo - Ciwita Financiera</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Base Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; /* Modern, clean sans-serif font for body text */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 30px; /* Adjust padding for better visual margins */
      color: #333; /* Softer black for better readability */
      line-height: 1.8; /* Increased line height for better readability */
      background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Light grey background for a professional feel */
    }

    /* Container for the contract content */
    .contract-container {
      max-width: 800px; /* Optimal width for readability on larger screens */
      margin: 40px auto; /* Centered with more vertical margin */
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #fff; /* White background for the contract area */
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; /* Subtle border */
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Soft shadow for depth */
      border-radius: 8px; /* Slightly rounded corners */
    }

    /* Title Styling */
    .title {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; /* A more traditional, strong serif font for the title */
      text-align: center;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 28px; /* Larger, more impactful title */
      font-weight: 700; /* Bold */
      color: #0f4c75; /* A deep, professional blue */
      margin-bottom: 40px; /* More space below the title */
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #0f4c75; /* A strong bottom border for emphasis */
      letter-spacing: 1.5px; /* Slight letter spacing for a refined look */
    }

    /* Section Styling */
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 30px; /* Increased margin between sections */
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #e0e0e0; /* Lighter, dashed separator */
    }

    .section:last-of-type {
      border-bottom: none; /* No border on the last section */
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600; /* Semi-bold for section headings */
      color: #0f4c75;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3282b8; /* A colored left border for emphasis */
      padding-left: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* Table Styling for Data Sections (Excel-like) */
    .data-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse; /* Ensure borders are clean */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #cce0ec; /* Light blue border for the whole table */
      display: block; /* Make table scrollable on small screens */
      overflow-x: auto; /* Add horizontal scrollbar if needed */
      white-space: nowrap; /* Prevent content from wrapping inside cells on small screens */
    }

    .data-table thead th {
        background-color: #eaf4fa; /* Light blue background for header */
        color: #0f4c75; /* Dark blue text for header */
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: left;
        padding: 12px 15px;
        border: 1px solid #cce0ec;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    .data-table tbody td {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border: 1px solid #e0eaf1; /* Lighter blue border for cells */
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      vertical-align: top; /* Align content to the top */
    }

    .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
        background-color: #f9fcff; /* Very light blue for even rows */
    }
    
    /* Revert table display for larger screens */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .data-table {
            display: table;
            overflow-x: visible;
            white-space: normal;
        }
    }


    /* Disclaimer/Commitment Text */
    .commitment-text {
      background-color: #f2f7fc; /* Light blue background */
      border-left: 5px solid #3282b8; /* Emphasized left border */
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px; /* Space above the text */
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      border-radius: 4px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .commitment-text strong {
      color: #0f4c75; /* Highlight client's name */
    }

    /* Signature Section */
    .signature-section {
      margin-top: 60px; /* More space above signatures */
      display: flex; /* Use flexbox for potential multiple signatures side-by-side */
      justify-content: space-around; /* Distribute signatures evenly */
      flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow signatures to wrap on smaller screens */
    }

    .signature-block {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px; /* Space around each signature block */
      flex: 1 1 300px; /* Allows blocks to grow/shrink but not smaller than 300px */
      max-width: 400px; /* Max width for each block */
    }

    .signature-line {
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      width: 80%; /* Width relative to its container */
      margin: 10px auto 5px auto; /* Centered line with some margin */
      padding-top: 5px;
    }

    .signature-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Responsive Adjustments */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        padding: 15px;
      }
      .contract-container {
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 25px;
        box-shadow: none; /* Reduce shadow on small devices */
        border: none; /* Reduce border on small devices */
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .section-heading {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .data-table thead th,
      .data-table tbody td {
          padding: 8px 10px; /* Smaller padding for cells on mobile */
          font-size: 14px; /* Slightly smaller font for mobile readability */
      }
      .commitment-text {
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .signature-section {
        flex-direction: column; /* Stack signature blocks vertically */
        align-items: center;
      }
      .signature-block {
        margin: 15px 0;
        width: 100%; /* Full width for signature blocks */
        max-width: 300px; /* Limit max width even when full width */
      }
    }

    /* Print Specific Styles */
    @media print {
      body {
        background-color: #fff; /* White background for printing */
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; /* Ensure colors print correctly */
        color-adjust: exact;
        margin: 0; /* No outer margin for printing */
        padding: 0; /* No outer padding */
      }
      .contract-container {
        box-shadow: none;
        border: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20mm; /* Use standard print margins */
        max-width: 100%; /* Use full available width */
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #000; /* Black border for print clarity */
        color: #000; /* Black text for print clarity */
      }
      .section-heading {
        color: #000; /* Black text for print clarity */
        border-left-color: #000; /* Black border for print clarity */
      }
      .data-table thead th {
        background-color: #e0e0e0 !important; /* Light grey for header background */
        color: #000 !important;
        border-color: #000 !important;
      }
      .data-table tbody td {
        border-color: #666 !important; /* Darker border for print contrast */
        color: #000 !important;
      }
      .data-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
        background-color: #f0f0f0 !important; /* Light grey for alternating rows */
      }
      .commitment-text {
        background-color: #f0f0f0 !important; /* Light grey background for printing */
        border-left-color: #666 !important; /* Darker border for contrast */
        color: #000 !important;
      }
      .commitment-text strong {
        color: #000 !important;
      }
      .label, .value {
        color: #000 !important; /* Black text for print clarity */
      }
      .signature-line {
        border-color: #000;
      }
      .signature-label {
        color: #000;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="contract-container">
    <div class="title">Contrato de Solicitud de Préstamo</div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3 class="section-heading">Información del Cliente</h3>
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Campo</th>
            <th>Valor</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Nombre completo</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cliente_nombre %> <%= prestamo.cliente_apellidos %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Apodo</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cliente_apodo || 'N/A' %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Cédula</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cliente_cedula %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Teléfono</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cliente_telefono1 %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Dirección</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cliente_direccion %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3 class="section-heading">Detalles del Préstamo</h3>
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Campo</th>
            <th>Valor</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Ingresos Mensuales</td>
            <td>RD$ <%= Number(prestamo.ingresos_mensuales).toLocaleString('es-DO', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Fecha de Solicitud</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.created_at ? new Date(prestamo.created_at).toLocaleDateString('es-DO') : 'Sin fecha' %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Monto Solicitado</td>
            <td>RD$ <%= Number(prestamo.monto_solicitado).toLocaleString('es-DO', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Monto Aprobado</td>
            <td>RD$ <%= Number(prestamo.monto_aprobado || 0).toLocaleString('es-DO', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Monto de Cuota</td>
            <td>RD$ <%= Number(prestamo.monto_por_cuota || 0).toLocaleString('es-DO', { minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2 }) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Forma de Pago</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.forma_pago %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Cuotas</td>
            <td><%= prestamo.cuotas %></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h3 class="section-heading">Términos y Condiciones</h3>
      <p class="commitment-text" style="text-align: justify;">
        Yo, <strong><%= prestamo.cliente_nombre %> <%= prestamo.cliente_apellidos %></strong>, con cédula de identidad y electoral número <%= prestamo.cliente_cedula %>,
        por medio del presente, me comprometo formalmente a pagar el préstamo aprobado bajo las condiciones establecidas, en el plazo y forma de pago
        indicados anteriormente. En caso de incumplimiento de cualquier cuota, acepto y reconozco un recargo por mora del <strong>5% diario</strong>
        a partir del segundo día posterior al vencimiento de la cuota correspondiente. Este contrato representa mi consentimiento expreso y mi compromiso inquebrantable
        con las obligaciones financieras adquiridas.
       
        <br><br>
        Asimismo, reconozco que de persistir la falta de pago, me comprometo a responder con cualquier bien de mi propiedad 
        (muebles, inmuebles, vehículos u otros) como garantía para saldar la deuda, autorizando expresamente a Financiera Caribe Azul a iniciar las acciones legales y/o judiciales correspondientes para recuperar el monto adeudado.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
      <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p class="signature-label">Firma del Cliente</p>
        <p class="signature-label">Fecha: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('es-DO') %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="signature-block">
        <div class="signature-line"></div>
        <p class="signature-label">Firma y Sello Financiera</p>
        <p class="signature-label">Fecha: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('es-DO') %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>